Any advice would be appreciated.

**UPDATE:** Just for good measure, I also tried the following in vain (same result):

 - 64-Bit
 - Console Application
 - LINQPad

Please note that the library needs to be activated: `Luxand.FSDK.ActivateLibrary(@&quot;Activation Code&quot;);`


